data.title: NGO in Bangladesh
data.meta_description: NGO in Bangladesh  - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides contact information for several NGOs (non-governmental organizations) operating in Bangladesh, including their addresses, phone numbers, emails, and websites. The NGOs cover a wide range of activities including acid attack victim support, disability services, rural development, education, healthcare, and more. Contact details are provided for over 30 different organizations located across Bangladesh.
